Here is a list of CP2K files that have been edited to interface with the MixPI code. These files should be copied to the cp2k/src folder
and CP2K should be recompiled. None of the edits performed to these files prevent CP2K from running as normal. Versions of these updated
files are available for two different versions of CP2K (2025.2 and 2023.2).

constraint.F
constraint_vsite.F
start/libcp2k.F
subsys/molecule_kind_types.F
topology_util.F
topology_psf.F
topology_generate_util.F
topology_connectivity_util.F
topology_coordinate_util.F
topology_types.F


